== 用途 ==
作为水果栽培的杏组物种主要是[[杏|杏]]。另外，中亚的[[紫杏|紫杏]]和中国的[[东北杏|东北杏]]、[[李梅杏|李梅杏]]、[[洪坪杏|洪坪杏]]、[[梅|梅]]亦作为水果栽培。<ref name=":0">{{Cite book|last=Lu|first=Lingdi|url=http://flora.huh.harvard.edu/china/PDF/PDF09/Armeniaca.PDF|title=Flora of China|last2=Bartholomew|first2=Bruce|publisher=Science Press & Missouri Botanical Garden Press|year=2003|editor-last=Wu|editor-first=Z.Y.|volume=9|location=Beijing & St. Louis|pages=396-401|chapter=''Armeniaca'' Scopoli|editor-last2=Raven|editor-first2=P. H.|editor-last3=Hong|editor-first3=D.Y.|access-date=2021-02-17|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304110332/http://flora.huh.harvard.edu/china/pdf/PDF09/Armeniaca.PDF|dead-url=no}}</ref>

[[杏仁|杏仁]]主要取自[[杏|杏]]、[[山杏|山杏]]、[[东北杏|东北杏]]，供食用或药用。

